+--------------------+
|  React Frontend    |
|  - Upload PDF      |
|  - Ask Question    |
+--------------------+
          |
          v
+--------------------+
| Express Backend    |
| Routes:            |
| /api/upload        |
| /api/query         |
+--------------------+
          |
          v
+--------------------+
| Upload Controller  |
| - Receive PDF      |
| - Extract text     |
| - Chunk text       |
| - Generate embeddings (nomic-embed-text) |
| - Store in MongoDB |
+--------------------+
          |
          v
+--------------------+
| Vector DB / MongoDB|
| - Stores text chunks + embeddings |
+--------------------+
          |
          v
+--------------------+
| Query Controller   |
| - Receive student question |
| - Embed question (nomic-embed-text) |
| - Compute similarity vs stored chunks |
| - Retrieve top relevant chunks |
| - Build context text |
| - Send context + question to Mistral |
+--------------------+
          |
          v
+--------------------+
| Mistral AI         |
| - Generates answer based on context |
+--------------------+
          |
          v
+--------------------+
| React Frontend     |
| - Display answer   |
+--------------------+
